<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id77fbfb48-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2022—Subsec. (c). <ref href="/us/pl/117/328">Pub. L. 117–328</ref> added subsec. (c).</p>
